These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Cigar: game, baccarat
Movie-Genre: crime, spy
Sport: cycling, surfing
Birthday: january, october
1. Birthday:october is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3
2. Cigar:baccarat is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:spy == Cigar:game##1
4. Birthday:october is on the right of Birthday:january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Cigar      | game  | baccarat   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Birthday     | january | october    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, cabbage
Birthday: august, march
Pet: dog, rat
Flower: balloon-flower, sunflower
1. Pet:rat is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:august == Flower:sunflower##1
3. Food:cabbage is on the right of Birthday:march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Birthday   | march | august  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Flower     | balloon-flower   | sunflower    |

 #################################
 
